OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772549421
OL,3,CRoyal Assent on mother and baby homes
OL,4,CBill expected to be granted
OL,6,FRoyal Assent is expected to be granted
OL,7,Fon the mother and baby homes Bill this
OL,8,Fsummer.
OL,10,FThe passing of the legislation will
OL,11,Fallow the opening of a public inquiry
OL,12,Finto the former institutions in
OL,13,FNorthern Ireland, as well as a redress
OL,14,Fscheme for victims and survivors.
OL,16,FMore than 14,000 women and girls are
OL,17,Fthought to have passed through
OL,18,Finstitutions, which were run by the
OL,19,FCatholic Church, religious orders,
OL,20,Fsome Protestant denominations, and the
OL,21,Fstate.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772549421
OL,3,CRoyal Assent on mother and baby homes
OL,4,CBill expected to be granted
OL,6,FMany were found to have been
OL,7,Fmistreated, held against their will
OL,8,Fand forced to give up their children
OL,9,Ffor adoption.
OL,11,FThe Inquiry (Mother and Baby
OL,12,FInstitutions, Magdalene Laundries and
OL,13,FWorkhouses) and Redress Scheme Bill
OL,14,Fhas reached the consideration stage in
OL,15,Fthe Northern Ireland Assembly process.
OL,17,FA payment of #10,000 is proposed to be
OL,18,Fmade to eligible claimants and a
OL,19,F#2,000 payment to eligible family
OL,20,Fmembers on behalf of a loved one who
OL,21,Fhas died since September 29 2011.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772549421
OL,3,CRoyal Assent on mother and baby homes
OL,4,CBill expected to be granted
OL,6,FThere have been calls for it to be
OL,7,Fdoubled to #20,000.
OL,9,FThere has also been criticism of the
OL,10,Ftimeframes for eligibility to apply
OL,11,Ffor redress, with a call to extend the
OL,12,Ftimescale to include those admitted
OL,13,Ffrom 1922 onwards.
OL,15,FAsked for an update during Executive
OL,16,FOffice questions, Junior Minister
OL,17,FJoanne Bunting said they aim to
OL,18,Fcomplete all the stages before the
OL,19,Fsummer recess, and anticipate Royal
OL,20,FAssent "during the summer months".
OL,26,@|D@HOU|D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772549421
OL,3,CRoyal Assent on mother and baby homes
OL,4,CBill expected to be granted
OL,6,FShe also said that preparatory work on
OL,7,Fthe necessary secondary legislation is
OL,8,F"progressing well".
OL,10,F"We plan to consult on these shortly
OL,11,Fafter the final vote, with the
OL,12,Fintention of opening the redress
OL,13,Fscheme before the end of the year, and
OL,14,Fthis will represent another important
OL,15,Fset of milestones to provide victims
OL,16,Fand survivors with truth and
OL,17,Facknowledgement," she said.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@RO]rD@AOUyD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
