OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772549421
OL,3,CRoyal Assent on mother and baby homes
OL,4,CBill expected to be granted
OL,6,FMs Bunting said the inquiry will open
OL,7,F"as soon as possible" after the
OL,8,Frelevant primary and secondary
OL,9,Flegislation comes into force.
OL,11,F"Victims and survivors have been at
OL,12,Fthe heart of this process from the
OL,13,Fvery beginning," she said.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@UO]sD@AOUuD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772549421
OL,3,CRoyal Assent on mother and baby homes
OL,4,CBill expected to be granted
OL,6,F"There will be consultation following
OL,7,Fthe final passage of this Bill on the
OL,8,Fnext steps and around the statutory
OL,9,Fthe rules of the inquiry, to ensure
OL,10,Fthat the concerns that victims and
OL,11,Fsurvivors have will be addressed and
OL,12,Falso that they are heard and listened
OL,13,Fto by the consultative forums."
OL,15,FAsked about progress on the redress
OL,16,Fscheme, Ms Bunting said the intention
OL,17,Fis to launch the redress service later
OL,18,Fthis year, subject to the passage of
OL,19,Fthe legislation.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772549421
OL,3,CRoyal Assent on mother and baby homes
OL,4,CBill expected to be granted
OL,6,F"In the interim, a shadow redress
OL,7,Fservice has been established within
OL,8,Fthe Department of Justice," she said.
OL,10,F"This team includes officials with
OL,11,Fexperience from other redress schemes
OL,12,Fwho bring valuable expertise and
OL,13,Fworking in a trauma-informed way.
OL,15,F"The current work is centred on
OL,16,Fdeveloping the IT system, progressing
OL,17,Fstaff recruitment and developing the
OL,18,Fsupport model so that everything is
OL,19,Fready to go."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@[O]rD@AOUwD@AOU{D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772549421
OL,3,CRoyal Assent on mother and baby homes
OL,4,CBill expected to be granted
OL,6,FShe said work is also ongoing in terms
OL,7,Fof access to records.
OL,9,F"We're aware that many have faced real
OL,10,Fobstacles and difficulties in trying
OL,11,Fto understand or trace their family
OL,12,Fhistory," she said.
OL,14,F"Work has been ongoing to improve that
OL,15,Fexperience and make those processes as
OL,16,Fstraightforward and actually
OL,17,Fsupportive as possible.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@IO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/10
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
