OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,447,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F446A1772549421
OL,3,CRoyal Assent on mother and baby homes
OL,4,CBill expected to be granted
OL,6,F"Applicants to the scheme will have
OL,7,Fpractical support from the Victims and
OL,8,FSurvivors Service, Wave and Adopt NI,
OL,9,Fto help them navigate what can be a
OL,10,Fdifficult and emotional process.
OL,12,F"We're also working closely with the
OL,13,FPublic Records Office in Northern
OL,14,FIreland on digitising records, and
OL,15,Fwith the trusts and Department of
OL,16,FHealth on managing any resourcing
OL,17,Fpressures so that resources can be
OL,18,Fcreated and provided as efficiently as
OL,19,Fpossible."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU{D@JO]
